item.title: H e l p im sick and tired!
item.dc:creator: @RahuX RahuX
item.description:
@RahuX wrote:

With Hamachi, create a new network and tell your friends to join it. Once they have joined your Hamachi network, run your server. Tell your friends to put your Hamachi IP in the New Server box. Then put the port it says on your runserver.bat window in the New Port box. It’s simple when you know how.
